Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.53,0:00:02.40,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}从上一集的《终空》里我们得知\N{\fs40\b0}Previously on "Final Space"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:05.40,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}夜幕揭晓了自己其实是来自未来的奎恩？！\N{\fs40\b0}Nightfall reveals that she's Quinn? From the future?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:06.92,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我的天哪\N{\fs40\b0}Whoa! Hot diggity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.96,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}而且  她对盖瑞很有意思\N{\fs40\b0}Also, she has a thing for Gary,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:11.03,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}然而没空搞太空3P了\N{\fs40\b0}but there's no time for cosmic three-ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:15.03,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}因为我们的队员们要去修补太空缺口\N{\fs40\b0}because our crew has a breach to close in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:16.33,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}时间紧迫呐\N{\fs40\b0}and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:23.31,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  你还有2分钟氧气可用\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, you have two minutes of oxygen left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:28.11,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}咱能...\N{\fs40\b0}Can we...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:30.71,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}换点高兴的话题吗？\N{\fs40\b0}change that to something more cheerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.51,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好的  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}Sure, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:33.75,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}饼干\N{\fs40\b0}Cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:36.32,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}假装你在烤一大堆饼干吧\N{\fs40\b0}Act like you're baking a big batch of cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:39.92,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  还有两分钟饼干就要烤好了\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, the cookies will be done in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:45.06,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦... 好极了  我喜欢饼干\N{\fs40\b0}Oh... fantastic. I love cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:47.66,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你烤的是什么饼干？\N{\fs40\b0}What kind of cookies we talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.73,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}奶油全麦饼干\N{\fs40\b0}Butter wheat crunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:52.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那个... 那个不能算饼干\N{\fs40\b0}That's... not a cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:56.70,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你知道的  HUE  你知道的！\N{\fs40\b0}And you know that, H.U.E. You know that!
