Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.23,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}大家！\N{\fs40\b0}Crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:32.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}或者说“把烂脾气的暴力薰心的\N{\fs40\b0}Or legion of murdering an irritatingly power-thirsty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:35.94,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}矮子恶魔打成屁眼筛子军团”！\N{\fs40\b0}pint-sized imp into a plethora of buttholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:38.08,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你们准备好拯救地球了吗！\N{\fs40\b0}Are you ready to save the Earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.28,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 好啊！好极了！   - 好！好啊！\N{\fs40\b0}- Hooray! Oh, yeah! - Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:42.81,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}问题是  队长大人  你准备好了吗？\N{\fs40\b0}The question is, Captain, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:44.68,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我早就准备好了！\N{\fs40\b0}I'm so ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:48.02,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好个大头鬼！我上哪拯救地球去？\N{\fs40\b0}I'm so not ready! How am I gonna save an entire planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.52,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我只是在尝试\N{\fs40\b0}I'm all for trying,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:53.36,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们很可能最后都死翘翘了\N{\fs40\b0}but there's a high chance we're all going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:55.89,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}或多或少  这已经是做成的买卖了\N{\fs40\b0}Yes. It's more or less a done deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:57.96,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这一点都没安慰到我！\N{\fs40\b0}That's not comforting at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:02.43,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我能做到的  对吧？对吧？！哦  根本不可能的！\N{\fs40\b0}I can do this, right? Right?! Oh, this is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:07.51,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}只要用心  就没有不可能的事\N{\fs40\b0}Nothing is impossible if we apply our minds to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:10.98,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE  你知道任何一种可以修补缺口的方法吗？\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., do we know of a way we can close this breach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:11.58,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我不知道\N{\fs40\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:12.78,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好吧  这就不好玩了\N{\fs40\b0}Well, that's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.61,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}或者... 你知道随便什么我们该做的事吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Okay, uh, well... anything at all we could do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.12,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这我知道  你可以亲亲自己的脸蛋  和自己告别\N{\fs40\b0}Yes. You can kiss your cheeks goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.48,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你丫耍我？\N{\fs40\b0}You givin' me a little clap back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:21.59,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你丫竟然耍我  HUE？！\N{\fs40\b0}You givin' me the old clap back, H.U.E.?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:25.26,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}在内爆成一团虚无之前  我们至少该试着做点什么\N{\fs40\b0}I thought I'd give it a try before we implode into nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.99,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他说“内爆成一团虚无”！\N{\fs40\b0}"Implode into nothingness," he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.86,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦我的老天啊  大周一的\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, my gosh. Freaking Mondays.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:36.50,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 盖瑞  我会死吗？   - 你是在给我振奋精神吗  KVN？\N{\fs40\b0}- Gary, am I gonna die? - Are you trying to cheer me up, KVN?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:39.80,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}能看到你死真是太棒了\N{\fs40\b0}Okay, because you dying would be a wonderful development.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:41.94,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}♪ 我们都将死去 ♪\N{\fs40\b0}♪ We're all gonna die ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.24,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}♪ 我们都将死... ♪\N{\fs40\b0}♪ We're all gonna di... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.48,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}给我闭嘴  KVN  不然我会想办法让你闭嘴的\N{\fs40\b0}Shut the hell up, KVN. Or I will find ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:49.15,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}其实还是有一种方法的\N{\fs40\b0}Actually, there is a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:53.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE  把目标定在12区  6.79域\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., set coordinates for sector 12, region 6.79.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:56.82,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}夜幕  我们会直接冲进猎户星云\N{\fs40\b0}Nightfall, that would fly us directly into the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.39,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}中央的主星的\N{\fs40\b0}at the heart of the Orion Nebula.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:02.09,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 我知道   - 我们不能往那飞！\N{\fs40\b0}- I know. - We are not flying into a sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:04.79,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 你想活下去吗？   - 我当然想\N{\fs40\b0}- Do you want to live? - Yes. I would love to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:08.50,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这也正是为什么我们不能往那里飞！\N{\fs40\b0}That's exactly freaking why we're not flying into a sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:11.04,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你说对了  我们不能飞进去  我们需要光折\N{\fs40\b0}You're right. We're going to lightfold in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:15.91,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这更不靠谱了！你说得好像这个方法更好似的\N{\fs40\b0}That's freaking worse! You said it like it was better,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:19.21,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 然而显然这个方法更烂！   - 我不建议这么干\N{\fs40\b0}- but that is the opposite of better! - I would never suggest this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.51,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}除非你还知道什么我不知道的秘密\N{\fs40\b0}unless I knew something you're not sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.61,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你还知道什么？\N{\fs40\b0}What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:26.52,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}奎恩  你不好奇你是怎么变成我的吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Quinn, aren't you curious how you became me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.92,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果答案包括冲着主星里面飞过去的话\N{\fs40\b0}If that answers even involves flying into a sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.42,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我一点都不好奇  我觉得是个人都不会好奇的\N{\fs40\b0}I'm not curious. I don't think anybody's curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:32.89,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 啊！   - 我很好奇！快说！\N{\fs40\b0}- Aah! - I'm curious! Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:34.49,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你非要这样吗  KVN？！\N{\fs40\b0} Must you, KVN?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:36.39,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 你非要这样吗？   - 嘿嘿嘿\N{\fs40\b0}- Must you?! - Hee-hee hoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:40.13,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 告诉我   - 只有一个生物能帮到我们\N{\fs40\b0}- Tell me. - There's only one being who can help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.63,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那就是一个居住在“内空”的泰坦\N{\fs40\b0}A Titan who inhabits a realm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.40,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}“内空”位于我们的次元和另一个次元之间\N{\fs40\b0}between our dimension and the next called Inner Space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:48.61,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他在我人生的低谷找到了我\N{\fs40\b0}He came to me. At my lowest point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:59.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}结束了  全都结束了\N{\fs40\b0}It's over. Everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.32,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我来了  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}I'm coming, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:07.02,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这并非你的命运\N{\fs40\b0}This is not your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:11.06,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我带来的不是癫狂  而是救赎\N{\fs40\b0}I offer not madness, but salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.10,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们能改变已经发生的事\N{\fs40\b0}We can change what has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:15.90,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}怎么改变\N{\fs40\b0}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.90,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}一台能时空转移的机器\N{\fs40\b0}A machine to traverse time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:22.57,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你可以自己搭一台  我会帮你\N{\fs40\b0}You can construct it. With my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.34,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你是谁？\N{\fs40\b0}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.04,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}波罗\N{\fs40\b0}Bolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.91,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我是无疆的受害者之一\N{\fs40\b0}A fellow victim of Infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:31.25,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们就要复仇了\N{\fs40\b0}And now we fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:34.19,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 波罗是谁？   - 他是个泰坦\N{\fs40\b0}- Who's Bolo? - He's a Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.52,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}泰坦是乐于复仇的可怖生物\N{\fs40\b0}The Titans are terrible, vengeful creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:39.26,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他们用混沌污染了宇宙\N{\fs40\b0}who poison the universe with chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.59,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}每个泰坦都分治不同的国度\N{\fs40\b0}Each in charge of a different realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.73,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}但其中一个打破了常规  那就是波罗\N{\fs40\b0}One broke ranks. Bolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.27,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他看到了更好的出路  因此封住了我们的次元\N{\fs40\b0}He saw there was a better way and sealed off our dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.33,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}让我们免于受到终空的威胁\N{\fs40\b0}from the horrors of Final Space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.27,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}泰坦们群起而攻之  把他囚禁了\N{\fs40\b0}They took revenge and imprisoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他是唯一能帮到我们的生物\N{\fs40\b0}He's the only one who can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:57.24,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这太可怕了\N{\fs40\b0}That's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.41,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}性感的老奎恩说得对\N{\fs40\b0}Older hot Quinn makes an excellent point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:03.91,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果波罗是唯一一个能帮我们的  我们只有这一个办法了\N{\fs40\b0}If Bolo's the only one that can help us, we've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:04.85,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Chookity pok!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:05.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}说得好  月饼\N{\fs40\b0}Well said, Mooncake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}让我们向着主星扎进去吧！\N{\fs40\b0}Let's fly through a sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:11.26,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦我的天哪  真不敢相信我们竟然要这么做\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, my Lord, I cannot believe we are doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.23,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}跨次元调整相位的难度众人皆知\N{\fs40\b0}Dimension phasing is notoriously difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.10,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}为了去见波罗  我们只能光折\N{\fs40\b0}To see Bolo, we're going to have to lightfold
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.97,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}而且必须精确穿过主星的光圈\N{\fs40\b0}exactly through the sun's aperture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:25.30,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哪怕只差了一度  我们也会坠火身亡\N{\fs40\b0}If we are off by even one degree, we burn up and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.84,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}请大家坐好  这段旅程将会非常崎岖\N{\fs40\b0}Buckle up. This will be a bumpy ride.
