Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:09.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}一直不知道咱俩同病相怜\N{\fs40\b0}Didn't know we were members of the same club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.92,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  你还要做这个吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, you still want to do this?
