Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.13,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}等等... 你刚是看了我和我爸吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Wait ... were you watching me and my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:22.56,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}没... 没有\N{\fs40\b0}No... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:32.40,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 你去哪？   - 他们不再需要我了\N{\fs40\b0}- Where are you going? - They don't need me anymore.
